Mark Lawson , 44 , was in The Diamond Tap public house in Newbury , Berkshire for his Christmas party when he agreed that his co-worker Simon Myers could take some chips from his plate .
However when Mr Myers started eating an onion ring , Lawson was angered , shouted at his victim and drove the knife into his thigh .
The knife tore into Mr Myers 's leg , causing a bloody wound nearly two inches deep .